 150:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (+) Different sequential I2C interfaces are listed below:
 151:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (++) Sequential transmit in master I2C mode an amount of data in non-blocking mode using
 152:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_i2c.c ****             HAL_I2C_Master_Seq_Transmit_IT() or using HAL_I2C_Master_Seq_Transmit_DMA()
 153:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (+++) At transmission end of current frame transfer, HAL_I2C_MasterTxCpltCallback() is execut
 154:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_i2c.c ****             users can add their own code by customization of function pointer HAL_I2C_MasterTxCpltC
