 247:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (+) __HAL_I2C_CLEAR_FLAG: Clear the specified I2C pending flag
 248:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (+) __HAL_I2C_ENABLE_IT: Enable the specified I2C interrupt
 249:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (+) __HAL_I2C_DISABLE_IT: Disable the specified I2C interrupt
